data.description: Completely remodeled 3 bedroom /2-bathroom home with over 1400 SqFt.  Located minutes to I-95, Downtown Jacksonville, restaurants and more! The upgrades include: New Siding, Fresh interior and exterior paint, new wood, tile, and carpet flooring, new plumbing in 2018, electric panel was replaced in 2016, new electric outlets and switches, both bathrooms have been completely remodeled, kitchen upgraded with new cabinets, granite countertops & new Backsplash, new doors throughout the house, new lighting fixtures, wood fence placed in 2017, new title flooring added to front porch,  Knockdown texture in ceiling and walls, new Soffit and fascia Installed. Seller will pay at closing  up to $3000 towards buyer's closing costs and pre-paid items with a full price offer.
